OL,3,CSchool bus driver more than four times
OL,4,Cover drink drive limit spared jail
OL,6,FA school bus driver who was more than
OL,7,Ffour times the limit when he was
OL,8,Fdriving a bus "filled with school
OL,9,Fchildren" has narrowly escaped going
OL,10,Fto jail.
OL,12,FDescribing the offences by Peter Gray
OL,13,Fas "appalling", District Judge Mark
OL,14,FHamill said they could well have
OL,15,Fresulted in "catastrophic"
OL,16,Fconsequences.
OL,18,FHe told the 43-year-old the "only
OL,19,Fthing" saving him from a prison
OL,20,Fsentence was that he was undergoing a
OL,21,Fmental health crisis at the time.
