OL,3,CSchool bus driver more than four times
OL,4,Cover drink drive limit spared jail
OL,6,FAs Gray admitted two offences of
OL,7,Fdriving with excess alcohol within the
OL,8,Fspace of two months, once on the
OL,9,Fschool bus in March and again in Asda
OL,10,Fcarpark in May, the judge imposed an
OL,11,F18 month probation order along with
OL,12,F200 hours of community service and a
OL,13,Ffive year driving ban.
OL,15,FAt an earlier hearing at Newtownards
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court, Gray, from
OL,17,FDrumadoon Drive in Dundonald, entered
OL,18,Fguilty pleas to drink driving on 11
OL,19,FMay and 19 March this year.
