OL,3,CSchool bus driver more than four times
OL,4,Cover drink drive limit spared jail
OL,6,FOpening the facts of the offences on
OL,7,FWednesday, a PPS lawyer told the court
OL,8,Fit was around 4.30pm on 19 March when
OL,9,Fthe Education Board asked the police
OL,10,Fto go to the Ulster Hospital due to
OL,11,Freports that "a bus driver had been
OL,12,Fdriving while intoxicated".
OL,14,FThe bus was at the hospital, "there
OL,15,Fwere children on board" and when
OL,16,Fofficers spoke to Gray "he appeared
OL,17,Fintoxicated".
OL,19,FA blood sample was taken from him and
OL,20,Fan analysis gave a reading of 331,
OL,21,Fmore than four times the limit of 80.
