OL,4,Cover drink drive limit spared jail
OL,6,FTurning to the 11 May this year, the
OL,7,Flawyer said police were sent to a
OL,8,Freport of an RTC in Asda carpark in
OL,9,FDundonald and when they arrived, Gray
OL,10,Fwas in the driver's seat of a VW Golf.
OL,12,FHe failed an initial preliminary
OL,13,Fbreath test and an evidential sample
OL,14,Fgave a reading of 189, more than five
OL,15,Ftimes the legal limit of 35.
OL,17,FBefore defence counsel Conan Rea began
OL,18,Fhis plea in mitigation, Judge Hamill
OL,19,Fsaid the facts were "appalling" and
OL,20,Fcould have resulted in "catastrophic"
OL,21,Fconsequences.
