OL,6,FHe revealed that according to the pre-
OL,7,Fsentence report Gray "had thoughts of
OL,8,Fkilling himself and the children".
OL,10,FMr Rea told the judge "all of that has
OL,11,Fto be conceded", adding that having
OL,12,Fconsulted with Gray for quite some
OL,13,Ftime, "the factual matrix in this case
OL,14,Fis very concerning and appalling is
OL,15,Fprobably the best that can be said
OL,16,Fabout it, he accepts all of that".
